<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>PATHIAN KAN NGEIH HI</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Isreal pawlramcar ah, harnak phunkip tawngpah in
 Kan Pathian nih, an herhmi, vialte a pek
 An hmuhmi le, an theihmi, Pathian thilti, khawhnak kha
 An zuum ngamlo, buainak in an khat dih.

[C1]
   A va mak e, kan Pathian, kan cung I, a that ning hi
   Rel thiamtu caah cun, a sunglawi tuk e
   Nitin kan herhmi vialte, kan caah,, khua a khan dih
   A va sunglawi e, Pathian kan ngei hi.

[V2]
 Hi vawlei, buainak ramah, zumtu nun cu Bawipa nih
 A dang tein a kan hruai, a kut nem in
 Theithiam loin, mi tampi, thinpannak in, kan khat tawn
 Zumtu kan nun a buai tawn a poi e.

[V3]
 Kan cung mang-bawi kan Pathian
 Lunglawmhnak, bia kan rak chim
 Kan cung I, na thatnak thluachuah kan relah
 Na kut tthawnnak, khuaruahhar
 Kan caah, kan hnangamnak
 Na min sung-lawi kan thangthat, cung Pathian.</lyrics>
<key>E</key>
</song>